discussion_comments.comment_body:
Using !important in CSS should be avoided as it makes styles difficult to override and maintain. Consider using more specific selectors instead.
```suggestion
.monaco-workbench .part.editor > .content .gettingStartedContainer .test-banner.special-banner {
	background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff6b6b, #4ecdc4);
	color: white;
```

